    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Prints made from surfaces built up with liquid plastics on wood, metal, cardboard, or plastic supports. May be printed intaglio or relief.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
